2
00:00:10,177 --> 00:00:12,771
《聖經》前情提要
Previously on The Bible.

3
00:00:20,354 --> 00:00:22,527
起初
In the beginning,

4
00:00:22,606 --> 00:00:25,109
上帝創造天地
God created heaven and earth.

5
00:00:26,401 --> 00:00:30,531
然而人罪惡令他失望
Then human failings led him to destroy his creation.

6
00:00:30,614 --> 00:00:33,083
錯誤的選擇,錯誤的決定
Wrong choices, wrong decisions.

7
00:00:33,158 --> 00:00:36,378
從諾亞後，開始了一個新時代...
After Noah, a new beginning...

8
00:00:36,453 --> 00:00:39,127
和一個亞伯拉罕的承諾
and a promise for Abraham.

9
00:00:39,206 --> 00:00:40,879
上帝同我說話了
God has spoken to me.

10
00:00:40,958 --> 00:00:44,633
他將指引我們去新的家園
He will lead us to a new home.

11
00:00:44,711 --> 00:00:48,341
他保證我的後裔會多如繁星
He has promised descendants as numerous as the stars.

12
00:00:49,967 --> 00:00:54,017
但由埃及奴役，亞伯拉罕的後裔遭受了痛苦
But enslaved by Egypt, Abraham's descendants suffered...

13
00:00:56,598 --> 00:00:59,568
直到一個新的領袖出現
Until a new leader emerged...

14
00:00:59,643 --> 00:01:01,896
誰會成為以色列最偉大的英雄
who would become Israel's greatest hero.

15
00:01:01,979 --> 00:01:03,856
你是誰
Who are you?

16
00:01:03,939 --> 00:01:07,068
我是摩西
My name is Moses.

17
00:01:07,150 --> 00:01:11,371
上帝派我回來  給你們自由
God has sent me... to set you free.

18
00:01:11,446 --> 00:01:14,746
自由  他們能自由選擇成為奴隸還是死人
Freedom? They're free to choose...

19
00:01:14,825 --> 00:01:16,702
被奴役或是死亡
slavery or death!

20
00:01:18,161 --> 00:01:20,664
我這一生都被法老奴役
All my life, I have been Pharaoh 's.

21
00:01:21,456 --> 00:01:23,083
我再也不會是個奴隸了
I will never be a slave again.

22
00:01:23,166 --> 00:01:26,716
約書亞  上帝與我們同在
Joshua, God is with us.

23
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:29,973
賴德
Ride!

24
00:01:30,048 --> 00:01:32,518
耶和華
Lord!

25
00:01:36,346 --> 00:01:39,020
跟我走
Follow me!

26
00:01:44,021 --> 00:01:47,400
上帝讓我們擺脫了奴役
God has delivered us from slavery.

27
00:01:47,482 --> 00:01:50,656
去應許之地繁衍生息
We're going to live in the promised land.

28
00:01:51,695 --> 00:01:54,244
亞伯拉罕的夢想  我們的未來
Abraham's dream is our future.

29
00:01:54,323 --> 00:01:57,953
你是我們人民的未來  約書亞
You are our future now, Joshua.

30
00:01:58,035 --> 00:02:01,835
你必須延續上帝與亞伯拉罕子孫的夢想
You must take the land promised to Abraham.

31
00:02:01,913 --> 00:02:03,915
摩西帶領以色列人
Moses has led the Israelites...

32
00:02:03,999 --> 00:02:06,422
到應許之地的邊垂
to the edge of the promised land.

33
00:02:06,502 --> 00:02:09,880
在約書亞帶領下,他們要征服它
Under Joshua, they must conquer it.

34
00:02:10,357 --> 00:02:14,357
《聖經》
第03集-家園

35
00:02:17,137 --> 00:02:19,981
耶和華   摩西傳下這十誡時
Lord, I was with Moses...

36
00:02:20,057 --> 00:02:23,186
我和他在一起
when he handed down these commandments.

37
00:02:23,268 --> 00:02:25,145
我見證了這份聖約
I was witness to the covenant,

38
00:02:26,229 --> 00:02:28,732
見證了賜予我們聖潔國度的承諾
the promise of a holy nation.

39
00:02:31,735 --> 00:02:33,988
助我建立這個國度
Help me to forge that nation,

40
00:02:35,072 --> 00:02:38,918
領導你的子民繼承他們的土地
to lead your people to inherit their land.

41
00:02:40,369 --> 00:02:41,916
約書亞
Joshua!

42
00:02:52,047 --> 00:02:56,348
主帶我們離開了埃及
- The Lord brought us out from Egypt. - Right!

43
00:02:56,426 --> 00:02:58,303
他承諾將賜予我們這片土地
He promised us this land.

44
00:02:59,930 --> 00:03:01,432
很快
And soon,

45
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,523
就會是我們的了
it will be ours.

46
00:03:08,105 --> 00:03:09,607
過來
Come.

47
00:03:14,903 --> 00:03:18,077
你們準備好了嗎  -我們會搜查整個城市
- Are you ready? - We'll search the whole city.

48
00:03:18,156 --> 00:03:19,999
找一條能讓我進去的路
Just find me a way in.

49
00:03:20,951 --> 00:03:22,794
我們必須攻下耶利哥
We must take Jericho.

50
00:03:22,868 --> 00:03:26,590
這是我們與應許之地間唯一的障礙了
It's all that stands between us and the promised land.

51
00:03:58,947 --> 00:04:01,450
嘿   嘿
Hey. Hey!

52
00:04:01,533 --> 00:04:03,581
白天才能取水
You can only collect water in daylight.

53
00:04:03,660 --> 00:04:05,628
現在回家去  走  走
Go home now. Go. Go.

54
00:04:05,704 --> 00:04:07,581
待在家裡
Stay indoors.

55
00:04:07,664 --> 00:04:10,213
以色列人隨時可能進攻
The Israelites can attack at any time.

56
00:04:18,550 --> 00:04:21,895
喇合  我的小妓女
Rahab, my little whore.

57
00:04:27,225 --> 00:04:30,445
你在外頭做什麼   你知道這是不安全的
What are you doing out, hmm? You know it's not safe.

58
00:04:30,521 --> 00:04:31,862
挺安全的
Safe enough.

59
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:34,984
沒有人是安全的
No one is safe.

60
00:04:35,066 --> 00:04:37,034
我可以照顧自己
I can look after myself.

61
00:04:45,035 --> 00:04:46,628
回去吧
Go home.

62
00:05:10,853 --> 00:05:12,354
噓
Shh.

63
00:05:14,606 --> 00:05:17,028
你們在這兒做什麼   以色列人
What are you doing here? Israelites!

64
00:05:17,108 --> 00:05:18,234
出去  出去
Go. Go.

65
00:05:18,318 --> 00:05:19,945
以色列人  救命
Israelites! Help!

66
00:05:20,028 --> 00:05:21,200
以色列人
Israelites!

67
00:05:26,785 --> 00:05:28,128
哥哥
Brother.

68
00:05:30,747 --> 00:05:32,749
為了以色列
For Israel!

69
00:05:32,833 --> 00:05:34,176
為了以色列
For Israel.

70
00:05:53,603 --> 00:05:55,105
快
Quick.

71
00:05:58,692 --> 00:06:01,161
這邊  再來點人
Over here! Get more men!

72
00:06:03,029 --> 00:06:05,077
我們得躲進去  小心
We've got to get inside. Look out.

73
00:06:14,416 --> 00:06:16,464
決不能讓他們跑了
They must not escape.

74
00:06:16,543 --> 00:06:18,420
挨家挨戶搜
Go door to door.

75
00:06:24,217 --> 00:06:25,218
進去
In here.

76
00:06:25,302 --> 00:06:28,055
所有人  都回家去
Everyone, return to your homes.

77
00:06:31,892 --> 00:06:34,111
人呢
Hello?

78
00:06:36,688 --> 00:06:38,736
噓
Shh.

79
00:06:41,026 --> 00:06:43,779
安靜  我保證不會傷害他
Keep quiet, and I promise I won't hurt him.

80
00:06:47,657 --> 00:06:49,159
你發誓
Swear.

81
00:06:50,118 --> 00:06:51,620
是的
Mmm.

82
00:07:03,632 --> 00:07:06,727
-你們是以色列人  -你聽說過我們嗎
- You're Israelites.- You've heard about us?

83
00:07:06,801 --> 00:07:10,522
你們有個能呼風喚雨  分開眾海的神
You have a god who commands the winds and parts the seas.

84
00:07:11,306 --> 00:07:13,775
他讓我們擺脫奴役  
He saved us from slavery.

85
00:07:13,851 --> 00:07:15,318
我們是被他選中的子民
We are his chosen.

86
00:07:15,393 --> 00:07:17,521
這座城裡的百姓忌憚你們
This whole city is terrified of you.

87
00:07:17,604 --> 00:07:20,733
你們有如此神通廣大的神   我們怎麼可能打敗你們
How can we fight a people whose god can do that?

88
00:07:20,815 --> 00:07:22,692
開門  開門
Open up! Open up!

89
00:07:24,361 --> 00:07:26,455
-進去  -把門打開
Back inside. Open the door!

90
00:07:28,156 --> 00:07:30,659
這條路能出去嗎
Can we get out that way?

91
00:07:32,911 --> 00:07:34,913
幫幫我們  我們也會幫你的
Help us, and we will help you.

92
00:07:36,289 --> 00:07:37,791
走吧
Go.

93
00:07:37,873 --> 00:07:39,547
我會盡力拖延的
I'll stall them if I can.

94
00:07:39,626 --> 00:07:41,845
打開門
Open the door!

95
00:07:44,589 --> 00:07:46,262
跟我們一起走吧 
Come with us.

96
00:07:46,341 --> 00:07:49,515
不行  我還有家人
I can't. My family.

97
00:07:56,518 --> 00:07:58,987
我們軍隊攻進來的時候   把這個掛你在門上
When our army comes, hang this on your door...

98
00:07:59,062 --> 00:08:01,736
這樣他們就不會傷害你們
so they will know not to harm you.

99
00:08:03,942 --> 00:08:05,740
你將免於這場災禍
You'll be passed over.

100
00:08:12,325 --> 00:08:13,827
待在這兒
Stay here.

101
00:08:19,624 --> 00:08:21,126
約書亞
Joshua!

102
00:08:23,504 --> 00:08:27,053
告訴我  找到進城的方法了嗎   這突破口嗎
Tell me, did you find a way in? Is there a weakness?

103
00:08:27,132 --> 00:08:29,555
城牆上沒有
Not in the walls...

104
00:08:29,634 --> 00:08:32,228
但百姓心中有
but... in their hearts.

105
00:08:32,303 --> 00:08:34,397
約書亞  我們遇到一個女人
Joshua, we met a woman.

106
00:08:34,472 --> 00:08:37,351
她認為這座城已經被上帝拿下了
She thinks God has taken the city already.

107
00:08:37,434 --> 00:08:40,187
他們知道上帝與我們同在   都陷入恐慌  不戰自潰
The people melt in fear because they know he is with us.

108
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:42,318
上帝確實與我們同在
God is with us.

109
00:08:43,606 --> 00:08:45,449
但我們仍要想辦法進城
But we've still to find a way in.

110
00:09:06,463 --> 00:09:08,682
摩西
Moses,

111
00:09:08,757 --> 00:09:10,475
我的老朋友
my old friend,

112
00:09:12,886 --> 00:09:14,684
你接下來會怎麼做
what would you do?

113
00:09:28,318 --> 00:09:32,164
主啊  當我還是奴隸的時候
Lord, when I was a slave,

114
00:09:32,238 --> 00:09:34,457
你向我展現了你的愛與能力
you showed me your love and your power.

115
00:09:37,577 --> 00:09:40,000
你給了我新的生活
You have given me new life.

116
00:09:42,332 --> 00:09:44,005
現在你想讓我們回頭嗎
Would you have us turn back?

117
00:09:50,757 --> 00:09:52,976
你
Who...

118
00:09:53,051 --> 00:09:54,724
你是誰
Who are you?

119
00:09:56,137 --> 00:09:57,810
我祈禱你是幫助我們的
I pray you are with us...

120
00:09:58,848 --> 00:10:00,691
不是幫助我們敵人的
and not with our enemies.

121
00:10:02,393 --> 00:10:04,235
我是與神同在的
I am with God.

122
00:10:05,355 --> 00:10:07,153
耶和華軍隊的元帥
Commander of the Lord's army.

123
00:10:17,033 --> 00:10:18,910
我主有什麼話吩咐僕人
What does he ask of us?

124
00:10:18,993 --> 00:10:21,712
主為摩西把紅海分開
The Lord parted the waters for Moses.

125
00:10:26,042 --> 00:10:27,544
為你
For you...

126
00:10:41,641 --> 00:10:43,359
主將塌陷城牆
He will split rock.

127
00:10:45,061 --> 00:10:46,734
你必須這麼做
This is what you must do.

128
00:10:48,148 --> 00:10:50,901
你們的一切兵丁要圍繞這城   一日圍繞一次
March around the city once a day with all the armed men.

129
00:10:52,861 --> 00:10:55,205
六日都要這樣行
Do this for six days.

130
00:10:57,699 --> 00:10:59,326
抬著約櫃
Carry the Ark with you.

131
00:10:59,409 --> 00:11:03,209
裡面有神的戒律   這樣祂就與你同在
It contains God's commandments, and he is with you.

132
00:11:08,793 --> 00:11:10,795
第七日
Then, on the seventh day,

133
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:13,302
你們要繞城七次
march around the city seven times.

134
00:11:21,097 --> 00:11:24,522
祭司也要吹角
Then the priests should make a long blast' with a ram is horn.

135
00:11:24,601 --> 00:11:26,444
你們一聽見角聲
As soon as you hear the sound of the trumpet...

136
00:11:29,355 --> 00:11:31,278
眾百姓要大聲呼喊
All the people shall shout a great shout.

137
00:11:43,244 --> 00:11:44,837
他們來了
It's happening!

138
00:11:44,913 --> 00:11:47,086
榮耀將會降臨
Glory will come.

139
00:12:02,430 --> 00:12:05,024
他的確是這世界的造物主
He truly is the shaper of the world.

140
00:12:41,678 --> 00:12:44,272
我們要把這座城獻給主
We give this city to the Lord!

141
00:12:44,347 --> 00:12:46,224
耶利哥是我們的
Jericho is ours!

142
00:13:03,199 --> 00:13:07,171
只有妓女喇合與她家中所有的可以存活
Only Rahab the prostitute and her family may be spared,

143
00:13:07,245 --> 00:13:08,963
這是上帝的旨意
for God said she must be spared...

144
00:13:09,038 --> 00:13:11,883
因為她幫助了我們   因為她幫助了我們
- for the help she gave us. ...for the help she gave us.

145
00:14:18,608 --> 00:14:20,576
上帝
God...

146
00:14:20,651 --> 00:14:22,574
兌現了他的承諾
has kept his promise.

147
00:14:23,905 --> 00:14:25,407
只要我們遵從主
If we obey the Lord,

148
00:14:26,407 --> 00:14:31,129
萬事都可能
anything is possible!

149
00:14:31,203 --> 00:14:34,549
以色列  以色列
Israel! Israel!

150
00:14:34,624 --> 00:14:37,628
以色列  以色列
Israel. Israel.

151
00:14:37,710 --> 00:14:43,717
以色列  以色列
Israel! Israel!

152
00:14:50,181 --> 00:14:52,900
約書亞死後一百年
A hundred years after Joshua,

153
00:14:52,975 --> 00:14:57,321
以色列十二個部落遍布迦南
the 12 tribes of Israel have spread out across the promised land.

154
00:15:00,024 --> 00:15:01,947
嘿
Hyah!

155
00:15:02,026 --> 00:15:04,120
但他們四面楚歌
But hostile neighbours surround them.

156
00:15:05,154 --> 00:15:08,579
嘿   嘿
Hyah! Hyah!

157
00:15:08,658 --> 00:15:11,537
非利士人武器精良  訓練有素
Better armed and better trained,

158
00:15:11,619 --> 00:15:13,587
是以色列人最致命的威脅
the Philistines are the deadliest threat.

159
00:15:18,418 --> 00:15:21,672
由於缺少摩西和約書亞這樣傑出領袖的領導
Without great leaders like Moses or Joshua to unite them,

160
00:15:23,506 --> 00:15:28,138
以色列人必須倚仗被稱為"士師"的本土英雄
the Israelites must rely on local heroes called judges...

161
00:15:29,011 --> 00:15:30,854
參孫就是其中之一
people like Samson.

162
00:15:39,647 --> 00:15:41,320
母親  來
Mother, come.

163
00:16:12,972 --> 00:16:15,066
這種日子什麼時候才能到個頭啊
When will this all stop?

164
00:16:17,018 --> 00:16:18,520
我也不知道
I don't know.

165
00:16:19,395 --> 00:16:21,272
你必須反抗
You must fight them.

166
00:16:23,357 --> 00:16:25,610
那是上帝想讓你做的  參孫
It's what God wants you to do, Samson.

167
00:16:25,693 --> 00:16:28,195
那是上帝創造你的原因
It's why God created you.

168
00:16:30,072 --> 00:16:32,450
記住他的信使跟我說的話
Remember what his messenger told me.

169
00:16:44,086 --> 00:16:46,556
別害怕
Don't be afraid.

170
00:16:47,757 --> 00:16:51,387
雖然你不能生育  但上帝會允你一個兒子
Though you are barren, God will give you a son.

171
00:16:54,847 --> 00:16:56,724
感謝您
Thank you.

172
00:16:56,807 --> 00:16:58,434
不過仔細聽好了
Listen carefully.

173
00:16:58,519 --> 00:17:00,236
這是有條件的
There are conditions.

174
00:17:04,273 --> 00:17:06,822
你當謹記  不可飲酒
See to it that you drink no alcohol...

175
00:17:06,901 --> 00:17:09,199
不可吃不潔之物
and eat nothing unclean.

176
00:17:09,278 --> 00:17:11,530
兒子出生後
And when your son is born,

177
00:17:11,614 --> 00:17:14,493
他永遠不可剃頭
his hair must never be cut.

178
00:17:14,575 --> 00:17:18,546
這是他作為拿細耳人的標記
This will be the sign that the boy is a Nazarite.

179
00:17:18,621 --> 00:17:24,129
他自出生起  便歸上帝
He is given to God, from his birth to his death.

180
00:17:24,210 --> 00:17:29,091
他會從非利士人手中拯救以色列
He will begin to deliver Israel from the Philistines.

181
00:17:42,478 --> 00:17:46,358
你的力量源自上帝
Your strength comes from God.

182
00:17:48,985 --> 00:17:53,286
你背負著趕走非利士人的使命
Your duty is to drive the Philistines away.

183
00:18:05,126 --> 00:18:07,629
參孫沒有對抗非利士人
Instead of fighting the Philistines,

184
00:18:07,712 --> 00:18:11,888
反而愛上了一個非利士女子  並娶她為妻
Samson falls in love... and marries one.

185
00:18:25,146 --> 00:18:27,365
