just because she's a Philistine?

192
00:18:46,709 --> 00:18:50,464
你的愛能保護我們不被他們傷害嗎
Will your love protect us from them?

193
00:18:50,546 --> 00:18:54,722
參孫  參孫   參孫  參孫   參孫  參孫 
Samson! Samson! Samson! Samson! Samson! Samson!

